data.description: *** Assumable VA loan at 2.375*** Looking for that perfect home on a great side of town? This is the one!! This beautiful 4 bedroom / 2.5 bath home in the amazing Stillwater Ranch subdivision is sure to wow you! The home features an open floor plan with high ceilings throughout. Downstairs you will find wood floors/ceramic tile with a study, dining room, family room, kitchen, and utility room with washer/dryer connections. Upstairs you will find another living space with all four of your bedrooms. The home was built by Imagine homes and was constructed with energy efficiency is mind. The roof was recently replaced along with the water softener (comes with the home!!), and a new tankless water heater. The home is located perfectly within San Antonio with quick access to all of the major highways and grocery stores/ restaurants. The schools are also some of the best in the area and the elementary school is located within the community for a short drive! The home has been totally touched up and repainted (photos were prior to touch ups) as well where needed! This home is ready for it's new owners!
